## Project layout

```
src/                Bounded-context source (DDD)
  application/      Use cases, services, workflows
  domain/           Entities, value objects, interfaces
  infrastructure/   DB / network / driver adapters
  presentation/     CLI parsers, HTTP routers, entry points
tests/              unit / integration / e2e / performance
docs/               api / architecture / manual / plans
{{ ai_folder }}/{{ ' ' * (16 - ai_folder|length) }}Agent workspace (instructions, skills, agents)
```

Empty directories are prefixed with `_` until you put something in them
(e.g. `_e2e/` becomes `e2e/` once you add a file).

